{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "阿莱克西斯（星龙祭Ver.） 第2话 烛光点亮的幸福",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "呼，到子民们的村子了。\\n那就作为圣星使者\\n开始我的慷慨之举吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "具体要怎么做？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "我想想。先去帮助\\n真正有烦恼的人吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "有烦恼的人吗……\\n嗯？那是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "唉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "一脸无精打采的样子。\\n那就是我要拯救的人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "喂，那边的少年！\\n我驾到了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "驾到……你是谁啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "我啊、我！真正的王、\\n圣星使者阿莱克西斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "既是王又是圣星使者的\\n阿莱克西斯！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "没错。子民的叹息就是我的叹息。\\n来吧，尽情说出你的烦恼。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "咦？那个……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也许你会一时觉得摸不着头脑，\\n但他是认真的。\\n不妨和他说说你的烦恼？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "我爸爸他……\\n不跟我一起庆祝星龙祭。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "每年一到这个时候，\\n他都会忙着卖蜡烛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "原来如此。那就让我\\n和你父亲好好谈谈。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "诶，真的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "一言既出驷马难追！我们走，\\n尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊！等等，阿莱克西斯！\\n得先问清楚他父亲在哪里啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "买个蜡烛吧？\\n为庆祝星龙祭，\\n不买个蜡烛吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "不行啊，完全卖不出去。\\n怎么办才好呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "找到了！卖蜡烛的！\\n长得和他儿子特别像！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "你、你是什么人？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "我是真正的王、\\n圣星使者阿莱克西斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "哦、哦……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我是听你儿子说了情况\\n才过来的。\\n听说你不卖完蜡烛就不会回去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "嗯，是啊。\\n不靠这个赚钱就没法过年。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "所以我才在这里揽客，\\n可谁都不肯回头看我一眼。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔，明明路过的人这么多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且庆祝星龙祭\\n经常用到蜡烛，\\n我还以为会很畅销……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "肯定是去其它店买了。\\n唉，该怎么办才好？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "这简单。只要打动他们的内心\\n让他们来买就行了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "打动……内心？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "正好，尤蒂尔，\\n让你见识一下我的演讲吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "趁这个机会好好学学，\\n什么叫打动民心的演讲。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "经过的子民们啊！\\n倾听我的话语吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人1",
            "context": "哇啊！？吓我一跳。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人2",
            "context": "突然间搞什么啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "咦？他怎么不说话？\\n因为受到关注而紧张了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不……\\n因为阿莱克西斯一直不说话，\\n大家都好奇他接下来要说什么呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n这就是打动民心的演讲么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "诸位……你们见过黑暗吗？\\n伸手不见五指的真正的黑暗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "我曾经见过。\\n就在我被驱逐出境，露宿野外的时候。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "诸位想象一下，没有月亮的夜晚，\\n从远处传来魔兽的吼叫时\\n却是孤身一人……你们能忍受吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人们",
            "context": "（咽口水）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "这种时候急着送死的蠢货才会逞强。\\n人只有坦然承认自己的恐惧，\\n才能明智地活下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "那么，接下来又该如何？\\n承认恐惧之后……你来回答。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人1",
            "context": "我吗？唔……那个，\\n我不知道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "答得好！不知道的事\\n就该清楚地回答不知道。\\n这也是明智地活下去所必需的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "我来告诉聪慧的诸位。\\n接下来就该为恐惧做好准备，\\n想想直面黑暗时该如何是好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "人们都说，有备无患。\\n时刻有所准备总没有坏处。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "所以我劝诸位准备好蜡烛。\\n现在买好备着，\\n便随时可以应对黑暗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人3",
            "context": "但是为了庆祝星龙祭，\\n我早就买好蜡烛了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "你那蜡烛\\n肯定会马上用完吧？\\n庆祝之火与守护之火不同。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "如果想尽情庆祝，\\n就得同时备好守护之火！\\n用这蜡烛守护自身的安宁吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "此处聪慧的诸位！\\n现在就把这蜡烛纳入囊中吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人1",
            "context": "对啊……反正在这里\\n买了也不亏。好，我买！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人2",
            "context": "也给我一个。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人3",
            "context": "我也要我也要！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好厉害！刚才明明完全卖不动，\\n现在客人却蜂拥而至……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这就是阿莱克西斯的演讲……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "来，买到的人喊起来！\\n获得安宁吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01",
                "120092_01",
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "路人们",
            "context": "获得安宁吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "如何！完美地售罄了吧！\\n哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "谢谢您！\\n多亏了您，我可以过年了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "有时间跟我道谢，\\n还不如早点去你儿子那里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "和他一起庆祝星龙祭吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年的父亲",
            "context": "好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样就解决了一桩事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "是啊。不过只解决一桩可不够，\\n要解决百桩！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110022_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿莱克西斯",
            "context": "毕竟是我亲自出手嘛！\\n哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}